v11_5_17\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.5.17\" class=\"v11_5_17\">17</sup>At the king\u2019s command they quarried out great, costly stones in order to lay the foundation of the house with dressed stones. </span><span class=\"v11_5_18\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.5.18\" class=\"v11_5_18\">18</sup>So Solomon\u2019s builders and Hiram\u2019s builders and the men of Gebal did the cutting and prepared the timber and the stone to build the house.</span></p>\n</div>\n", 
